<html lang="en">
  <body>
    <p>
      You can test <code>file.ServeHTTP</code> responses with the file whose
      relative path is <code>public/index</code> for the request of
      <code>/</code> by requesting <code>/</code> and asserting it writes the
      content of this file.
    </p>
    <p>
      You can test <code>file.ServeHTTP</code> responses with
      <code>Content-Language: ja</code> by requesting <code>/</code> and
      asserting it sets the field.
    </p>
  </body>
</html>
